<seg id="849">In accordance with the wording of Law No 235/2004, which expires on 1 January 2005, the place of performance in the supply of electrical energy is the place of performance where the purchaser has his legal place of business, his place of business or his permanent establishment for which that supply is made.</seg>
<seg id="850">Therefore, the Czech taxpayers should not have indicated the electricity supplies in their ZM for 2005.</seg>
<seg id="851">The fact that both taxable persons treated the supply of electrical energy in their CpRs as intra-Community supplies led to a difference in the amount of CZK 503,881,939 in MIAS.</seg>
<seg id="852">Closing remarks</seg>
<seg id="853">The cooperation has achieved the objectives of the BRH and the NA.</seg>
