<seg id="199">Key test results</seg>
<seg id="200">Bhr</seg>
<seg id="201">Technical specifications and product-neutral tendering</seg>
<seg id="202">In individual cases, the service descriptions contained references to national technical approvals or standards which had already been replaced by Europe-wide standards.</seg>
